TO RUN:
Create .env file in 'server' folder and paste text from Discord.
Run the client side and server side commands below in two separate terminals.

--------------

Client side:

cd client
npm install
npm run dev

OR (works for Alex):

cd client
npm install
node .\node_modules\vite\bin\vite.js


Server side (works for Alex):

cd server
npm install
node .\node_modules\nodemon\bin\nodemon.js src/server.js
